title: About Vegan Gains (Anti-Racism, Cory & Tara McCarthy, etc.)
description:
Co-starring "VeganCalledQuest" on Younow: https://twitter.com/vegancalledQ
Apologies for the terrible sound quality (in fact, within the first few minutes of the video, I directly apologize for and explain the poor sound quality).
This video is a spontaneous, informal conversation: if you want to follow it up with a scripted, well-researched discussion of scientific racism ("Race and IQ", "The Bell Curve", J. Philippe Rushton, etc.) take a look at "Reading the Right — Volume One".  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GgZFGgJlAsk
